<bibRefCitation id="EFA94B29C6047128FC6BFDC8107E99B9" author="KIRBY W. F." box="[941,1054,631,655]" pageId="37" pageNumber="442" refId="ref35345" refString="KIRBY W. F. 1906. - A Synonymic Catalogue of Orthoptera. Volume II. Orthoptera Saltatoria. Part 1. Achetidae and Phasgonuridae. British Museum (Natural History), London, viii + 562 p." type="book" year="1906">Kirby 1906</bibRefCitation>
